data.description: Step into this stunning home that boasts 4 generously sized bedrooms and two full-sized restrooms. The residence is located on a quiet street. This house is great for entertaining and relaxing. In the backyard there is an in-ground pool and spa. A brand-new pump and filter were installed as part of recent maintenance on the spa and pool.  Greenery and a brand-new gazebo provide year-round shade in the backyard.  The obstructing fence in the backyard is great for privacy. There is a brand-new 10-by-12-foot shed included with this property.Landscape design for the front and back yards. This residence provides parking for RVs. Three-car garage and driveway parking are available.The owners of this residence have also installed a water softener extends the life of certain appliances, treats skin conditions, say goodbye to bad hair days, and much more. Rest easy with a comprehensive security system and front door camera that only requires activation.The kitchen has a central island and countertop that provide ample space for cooking and storage with fairly new kitchen appliances. his residence has been meticulously maintained and is move-in ready. Come and experience the cozy and welcoming atmosphere of this beautiful house.
